title: Marvel Heroic Roleplaying - Annihilation Event Book
description:
Marvel Heroic Roleplaying - Annihilation Event Book
===================================================

Format: PDF 
Language: English
First Published: 2013
Publisher: Margaret Weis Productions

Roleplay Marvel superheroes in this galactic adventure.

Now out of print due to Marvel pulling the licence from Margaret Weis Productions rather abruptly. This was only available for a very short time and only as a PDF.
